<span style=3D"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif=
&quot;;color:#111111">But of course the entire Trump phenomenon has nothing=
 to do with policy or ideology. It has nothing to do with the Republican Pa=
rty, either, except in its historic role as incubator
