 the storm pass, they insist, and then we can pick up
 the pieces, rebuild and get back to normal. Meanwhile, don=92t alienate th=
e leader=92s mass following. After all, they are voters and will need to br=
ought back into the fold. As for Trump himself, let=92s shape him, advise h=
im, steer him in the right direction and,
 not incidentally, save our political skins.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:13.5pt;ma=
